Package: context-manager
Version: 2.3.5
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: nodejs (>= 14.0.0), npm (>= 6.0.0)
Maintainer: Hakkı Sağdıç <hakkisagdic@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/hakkisagdic/context-manager
Description: Universal LLM context manager with method-level filtering
 Context Manager is a universal LLM context optimization tool with
 method-level filtering and exact token counting. It analyzes codebases
 in 14+ programming languages and generates optimized file/method lists
 for AI assistant consumption.
 .
 Key Features:
  * TOON format with 40-50% token reduction
  * 8 output formats (TOON, JSON, YAML, CSV, XML, Markdown, GitIngest)
  * Smart GitIngest chunking for large repositories
  * Interactive wizard and live dashboard (with Ink dependencies)
  * Method-level analysis for 14+ programming languages
  * Exact token counting with tiktoken
  * Format conversion utilities
  * Enterprise logging and auto-update system
